on or Code Review\n   555→\n   556→| Severity | Story | Issue | Status |\n   557→|----------|-------|-------|--------|\n   558→| HIGH | 14-1 | `generateSlug('')` returns empty string — malformed TD story keys | Fixed |\n   559→| HIGH | 14-1 | `backlogAppended` falsely reports success when `projectRoot` is omitted | Fixed |\n   560→| HIGH | 14-1 | `wordOverlap` exceeds 1.0 with duplicate words, breaking dedup contract | Fixed |\n   561→| HIGH | 14-4 | Missing CLI validation for `--observability-backend` — unsafe `as` cast | Fixed |\n   562→| HIGH | 14-6 | Time budget deferral was fire-and-forget — never killed agent process | Fixed |\n   563→| HIGH | 14-6 | `updateStoryStatus()` return value silently discarded | Fixed |\n   564→| HIGH | 15-1 | `.tsx` files excluded from CI file size gate | Fixed |\n   565→| MEDIUM | 14-4 | ELK compose file resolution pointed to Victoria compose | Fixed |\n   566→| MEDIUM | 14-4 | Wrong endpoints displayed for ELK backend (Victoria ports) | Fixed |\n   567→| MEDIUM | 14-4 | `resolveEndpoints()` not backend-aware | Fixed |\n   568→| MEDIUM | 14-6 | `shouldDeferPhase` returned false for NaN (unsafe default) | Fixed |\n   569→| MEDIUM | 15-1 | Empty SRC_DIR=\"\" scans project root instead of src/ | Fixed |\n   570→| MEDIUM | 15-1 | Trailing slash in SRC_DIR produces double-slash in annotations | Fixed |\n   571→| MEDIUM | 15-1 | No violation counts in output summary | Fixed |\n   572→\n   573→All HIGH and MEDIUM bugs were caught by code review and fixed before merge.\n   574→\n   575→### 2b. Workarounds / Tech Debt Introduced\n   576→\n   577→- **run.ts at exactly 300 lines** — zero margin. Any future addition requires extraction (14-3).\n   578→- **docker-setup.ts at exactly 300 lines** — same situation (14-4).\n   579→- **formatters.ts grew to 605 lines** — pre-existing violation, worsened by 23 lines (14-4).\n   580→- **NodejsProvider at 358 lines** — grew by 12 lines, pre-existing violation (14-5).\n   581→- **env.ts at 304 lines** —